                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18360613-1391-offence-1 t18360613-cd-11"></join>30th of April</rs>, 1 handkerchief, value 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18360613-name-166" type="victimName">
